demand reconstruction of original message content and digital seal time stamp and message authentication services it also provides esignoff service enabling the message recipients to electronically sign and timestamp emails and attachments econtract service that allows to electronically sign and timestamp an email message and attachment by creating a en rpost inc provides email delivery proof encryption and esignatures technology services for companies worldwide the company offers rmail services a registered email services platform to provide proof of email delivery content and official time legalproof records for proving legality of email registered receipt return email an ondemand reconstruction of original message content and digital seal time stamp and message authentication services it also provides esignoff service enabling the message recipients to electronically sign and timestamp emails and attachments econtract service that allows to electronically sign and timestamp an email message and attachment by creating a enforceable contract proof archive service a management tool to archive a copy of the evidentiary record of the email transaction in a master repository securmail an encryption email service register reply that records a backandforth discussion or negotiation with an internal or external party and sidenote which lets the sender to add context for cc and bcc recipients in the form of private comments and instructions on the original message in addition the company offers rpost cloud platform that processes legal electronic messaging largemail service enabling to attach up to mb of files per email message rpdf form a smart technology that captures clients mousescripted legal electronic signature or indication of acceptance of terms and certified email service an email service that provides the recipient of the certified email message with a means to authenticate the message origin author and content the company serves legal governments insurance agents and brokers insurance carriers real estate travel factoringabl auditing telecom carriers financial services franchise engineering and pharmaceutical companies the company was founded in  and is based in los angeles california rpost inc operates as a subsidiary of rpost communications ltd detailed description  west century boulevardsuite los angeles ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwrpostcom key executives for rpost inc mr zafar khan founder chairman and chief executive officer dr terrance tomkow founder chief technology officer and director mr luis zambrano vice president of finance  operations bart bonnevalle head of sales department  benelux region jane hastings head of legal vertical  london market compensation as of fiscal year  rpost inc key developments rposts update for rmail brings enhanced cybersecurity and collaboration features oct   rpost announced an extensive update has arrived to rposts cybersecurity product rmail the allinone service that empowers email users microsoft outlook and gmail interfaces with sending options including email encryption open tracking certified delivery proof esignatures and secure large file transfers rmail® has been relied upon for important messaging by governments and businesses of all sizes for more than a decade three new technologies inside the latest rmail product include antiwhaling™ imposter protection an automatic email encryption mode and secure file share large file transfer rmails antiwhaling imposter protection feature protects microsoft outlook users against whaling attacks also known as business email compromise bec attacks rpost has also made important changes to the email encryption functionality within rmail allowing for improved easeofuse without sacrificing security when sending an encrypted email message with rmail there is a new automatic mode for secure sending that automatically detects and selects the easiest secure sending method available considering the recipient user experience for each recipient destination in all situations rmail uses its patented true direct delivery™ encryption technology so that the recipient does not need to register for an account or go to a rd party website to retrieve the message content and there is no message storage in the middle or on the web rpost partners with broker network to offer rmail sep   rpost announced a new partnership with broker network to further assist more than  uk insurance brokers with secure email esignatures and auditable proof of email delivery all designed to assist brokers in complying with the new act rposts rmail service integrates seamlessly with microsoft outlook office  and gmail and can also be used via an ipad app or with backoffice web or crm integration options rpost technology has been endorsed for compliance and cyber security by broker networkand biba rpost inc presents at investment trends summit sep  am sep   rpost inc presents at investment trends summit sep  am venue four seasons resort the biltmore santa barbara  channel drive santa barbara ca  united states similar private companies by industry company name region atlantic telesatellite inc united states club domains llc united states comdaq corporation united states kache media management llc united states court united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored 